<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200925/f010e16f05314533861b271cc1e1b088.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">俗话说——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200925/ee2e653cd89e4895bd741766b4e38ac7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哈士奇的破坏力之所以这么惊人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还得追溯到它的<strong>祖先</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">远古时代的<strong>爱斯基摩人</strong>穿越北极圈在格陵兰落脚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此时咀嚼和挖掘能力超强的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>西伯利亚哈士奇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就充当人类的好帮手</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>夏天拉船，冬天拉雪橇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>白天跟人打猎，晚上看着牲畜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>还要经常面对恶劣的天气</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>996，715</strong>的生活让它们十分充实</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它们血管里流的都是<strong>鸡血</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>忙</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">已经刻进了它们的基因里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200925/ee901e895435499290ed9ec30cba7c9e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">时代发展</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哈士奇成为众多家庭里不可或缺的一员</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人类宠着它们，护着它们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200925/67c76bb480f94ee8858f970146cdcb5a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">至今它们还保留着<strong>追逐、打猎</strong>的原始本性</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在活动范围比较小的地方</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它们过剩的精力经常无法发泄</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200925/b46adb9f417c40a29929fffbee5882cd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200925/c9e65b3cbdcb42a181416bc5d544b2f7.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200925/6ea39970039a4dcca89ac392720d6507.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200925/93266755dff74b7682d6017ce1381b11.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200925/65b42ed252634dfc8e6afe73b5e6b686.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200925/1d8132125675476a8770e01ddb00ed90.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哈士奇精湛的拆迁技术</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大概就比人类厉害了<strong>亿点</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200925/99238c37f0834bcca1b9759cc822cf72.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200925/528867b061074f6cb39729d17c334b43.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200925/f93a2a9d7b7547a4a545f6d991b7f809.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200925/e2adb407c5b7448a948180e36f07e399.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“二”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个词给人的印象就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>智商不高</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200925/26990f7f69544d859383b89030e12899.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在世界犬类智商排名中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">128种犬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哈士奇可是排到第<strong>47</strong>位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">智商相当于2-3岁的孩子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱卿以为它傻傻的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实它是<strong>深藏不露</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200925/d4041f7d697346bbb9fc3de1a6a61d2c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200925/8664ed2cdb884c63995032805f002515.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">问题在于<strong>哈士奇的服从性比较低</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">换句话说就是哈士奇智商绝对不低</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只是懒得听人的话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这就造成哈士奇的画风跟其它狗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">别的狗狗能让人感天动地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200925/b6a7824e85a249d480b458607b858421.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哈士奇出脚就能让你<strong>惊天撼地</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200925/f335d6c8712b40d6a194034647a9bdfc.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让金毛跟哈士奇不对眼前的鸡腿动嘴</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>只有金毛在好好听话</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200925/e3895703917e454fb3d0322852d5d3e0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果让牧羊犬跟哈士奇参加比赛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哈士奇就能生动地诠释</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">什么叫<strong>到此一游</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实它们也会开锁哦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只不过是这样开的……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200925/47e14e505ba44874b2142d06aa446f4c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">据说凭哈士奇的<strong>第一顿饭</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就可以筛选出<strong>最优良的血统</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200925/c58f7ecac9b342f7b5bfeda7b74188d4.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哈士奇是如此疯狂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因此它们还常常</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">迷失自我</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它们可以跟羊驼一样<strong>欢乐跳跃</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200925/b7e52a666fad4f74a4020f20398682f3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以跟小羊一样<strong>吃草</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200925/21ceef6d45324802a4664a4f7c9213ff.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它们常常证明</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我的身体不是我的身体</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以吃自己的脚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200925/d3d8c8ec648040c6b33e395b9b2732c9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">咬自己的尾巴</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200925/658fb7592e124ffcb2c4ee622a2030c5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">四条腿也是<strong>各跑各的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200925/d3e4c1704e2f49ce96335a5fd2090967.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>自己玩死自己</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200925/a1deac9284ab4b0cac3cb6d080bf1ada.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它们连饭都可能不知道怎么吃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200925/19989f89ef104a9d956ee77b935fa1ab.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">西伯利亚哈士奇经常<strong>团队合作</strong>干活</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因此哈士奇天生就<strong>对同类很有好感</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果一只哈士奇真的对你很好</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那可能就说明……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200925/48e046c1d2cd4bbb9684e69ff567bc47.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">偶尔它们也会配合主人的演出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200925/a83b15016cf84383afd2641e0e326d0a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要说对主人的感情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那也是<strong>十分厚重</strong>的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200925/7150ab860eb34f8f96c38400f933fe92.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200925/3cf747de1e8d43dd93f59f75001a9612.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">既然哈士奇还有一些智商</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就算服从性差</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200925/a175d2b12250482bbecbeab773623b11.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那么可不可以多加训练</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>让它们克服缺点，发挥优点</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>当一只警犬呢？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200925/e22e905f364944149f7a38773b728677.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云南的某特警队和消防队</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就曾尝试训练两只哈士奇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过那真的需要<strong>手把手训练</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200925/8f83eb785fce4437b1ac2368742d8470.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200925/d684fae7a0f6431881359244e77492f0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而训练成果就是……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200925/9df24d85a1404ee09abc7af1fe0af0d9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200925/32f4d6961f164a10bdbe789fa8858638.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哈士奇还不忘发挥自己的本领</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200925/c3a12df12a1d4e47b2ba45e04b449366.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就连特警跟消防员都没办法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">真要哈士奇<strong>入编制还是很有难度</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200925/1f93ee3f67a1489eb7bf57969caee420.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就算不拆家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那也是养不起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200925/5ebcfe4e44684f1fa61b5f357a37cfe7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要说对付坏人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哈士奇被偷走时也是乖乖的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200925/224387b5afb2497b922ac47df40d801a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至可以围观小偷偷盗全过程</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并<strong>目送他离开</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200925/b61ecb01038c474b8577acfefcb47272.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200925/bf7b6617b02a45f28c8a1f4462eba962.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200925/0bef7dbcb32c4aa2a0bd1fa48c4b9680.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200925/119330e6cbb74c12807c0c29177fe88b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200925/9eb1c0dab8574dd583f527f2da309e18.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200925/670ddd35e1be4c1d8cc936eb903efebd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哈士奇虽然个性奇特</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但是也阻挡不了人类对它的喜爱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哈士奇不仅给人类拉雪橇干苦活</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还曾<strong>救过人命</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">1925年1月</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">美国阿拉斯加居民遭受到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>白喉</strong>（一种急性呼吸道传染病）的侵袭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">急需血清用于治疗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200925/aff84dfddc6648debde779677d2df447.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以当时雪橇犬正常的运送速度</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">得花25天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但由于患者急速增加</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">组织者决定采用<strong>接力</strong>方式运送血清</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哈士奇队仅用了<strong>5</strong>天的时间便完成了任务</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将血清送到了目的地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">挽救了人们的生命</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200925/031996b97ab846ae944cbc8b838f67af.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哈士奇队伍的领队犬当时已经10多岁了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以说是一只<strong>老年犬</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在完成任务后就因为<strong>腿伤</strong>退出了雪橇队</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">1929年12月</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这只哈士奇去世</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">纽约中央公园为了纪念这件事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就给它设了<strong>纪念碑</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200925/2bc69708b6fd4901ba1b87163f7e467a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">养哈士奇需要<strong>慎重</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅是因为哈士奇很二、撒手没</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还因为它能让你体验</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">什么叫六月飞雪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">什么叫蒲公英的约定……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200925/354c0a51212f47f89e2e6173faa77709.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
